.£Siempre que la Membrana de éter bloquee a una criatura, regresa esa criatura a la mano de su propietario al final del combate.',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'#_天国への門の姿を模すが、導く先は灰色の辺土だ。_#',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL),('122432','Akroma, Angel of Fury','PLC','Legendary Creature — Angel','R','{5}{R}{R}{R}','8','6','6',NULL,'This spell can''t be countered.£Flying, trample, protection from white and from blue£{R}: Akroma, Angel of Fury gets +1/+0 until end of turn.£Morph {3}{R}{R}{R} #_(You may cast this card face down as a 2/2 creature for {3}. Turn it face up any time for its morph cost.)_#',NULL,NULL,'Daren Bader','94','4.328','£2/1/2007: If Akroma, Angel of Fury is cast face down, it can be countered.£2/1/2007: Akroma, Angel of Fury and Akroma, Angel of Wrath do not have the same name, so the legend rule does not apply.£7/1/2013: In a Commander game where this card is your commander, you may cast it face-down from the Command zone by paying {3} plus {2} for each time it has been cast from your command zone. The cost to turn it face-up is unaffected.£3/16/2018: The “legend rule” cares about legendary permanents with the exact same English name. You can control Akroma, Angel of Fury and Akroma, Angel of Wrath at the same time.','R',NULL,'1','2.61','8',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'R','怒火天使爱若玛',NULL,'Akroma, ange de la Fureur','Akroma, Engel der Wut','Akroma, Angelo della Furia','憤怒の天使アクローマ','Akroma, Anjo da Fúria','Акрома, Ангел Бешенства','Akroma, ángel de furia',NULL,'传奇生物～天使',NULL,'Créature légendaire : ange','Legendäre Kreatur — Engel','Creatura Leggendaria — Angelo','伝説のクリーチャー ― 天使','Criatura Lendária — Anjo','Легендарное существо — Ангел','Criatura legendaria — Ángel',NULL,'怒火天使爱若玛不能被反击。£飞行，践踏，反白保护，反蓝保护£{R}：怒火天使爱若玛得+1/+0直到回合结束。£变身{3}{R}{R}{R}（你可牌面朝下地使用此牌并支付{3}，将其当成2/2生物。 可随时支付其变身费用使其翻回正面。）',NULL,'Akroma, ange de la Fureur ne peut pas être contrecarrée.£Vol, piétinement, protection contre le blanc, protection contre le